This directory should contain the Infinispan jars.

You do this by downloading the latest Infinispan 5.x release from http://sourceforge.net/projects/infinispan/files/infinispan

It is recommended that you download the bin.ZIP archive, such as infinispan-5.0.0.CR7-bin.zip

Extract this archive somewhere, and copy the necessary jar files to this directory.

     $ unzip -a infinispan-5.0.0.CR7-bin.zip -d /tmp
     $ cp /tmp/infinispan-5.0.0.CR7/infinispan-core.jar .
     $ cp /tmp/infinispan-5.0.0.CR7/lib/* .

The jar files you will need are:

  * infinispan-core.jar
  * jboss-logging.jar
  * jboss-marshalling.jar
  * jboss-marshalling-river.jar
  * jboss-transaction-api.jar
  * jgroups.jar





